  <brief_title>Relationship of Obesity With GERD Among Nigerians</brief_title>
  <official_title>Relationship Between Body Mass Index, Waist Circumference, Waist Hip Ratio and Erosive Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease in a Tertiary Centre in Nigeria: a Case Control Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
